<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-03-11</DATELINE><TITLE>Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19): Protecting Hospitals From the Invisible</TITLE><BODY>Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) is optimized to spread widely: Its signs and symptoms are largely indistinguishable from those of other respiratory viruses. This commentary specifically addresses best ways to protect our hospitals against COVID-19.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>